reviewText: My daughter loves Chloes Closet and enjoys watching this 3 DVD set. These cute little episodes are all about pretend play and they can be anything they want in Chloes world. A lot of the time I find they don't have the episodes listed or show the back cover that includes them. Since many kids have a favorite episode Im including the back cover photo.
Engaging children's show.  My daughter loves Chloe.  Nothing scary or violent, just happy life lessons/stories.
